Hyderabad ki itihasik kahani kai sau saalon tak phaili hui hai, aur yeh ek aisi sheher hai jiska itihas, sanskriti aur vikas kai dharon se juda hua hai. Hyderabad ka sthapna 1591 mein Quli Qutb Shah ne ki thi, jab unhone Golconda ke qile ke paas ek nayi sheher ki buniyad rakhi thi, jo jaldi hi unki Qutb Shahi sultanat ka ek mahatvapurn kendra ban gaya. 1687 mein, Mughal Badshah Aurangzeb ne Golconda par kabja kar liya, aur Hyderabad ko Mughalon ke under kar diya. Uske baad 18vi sadi mein, Nizam-ul-Mulk ne Hyderabad ko apna rajdhani banaya, aur Nizam ki hukumat 1948 tak chali, jab tak Hyderabad ko Bharat mein milaya nahi gaya. Hyderabad ka itihas iske shikshan, kala, aur vyavsayik vikas ke liye bhi jaana jaata hai, jaise ki itihasik Charminar, Chowmohalla Palace, aur Salar Jung Museum. Nizam ki sarkar ke dauraan, sheher mein bhut se infrastructural aur architectural vikas hue, jismein pehle Hyderabad-Deccan Railway, aur Harbinger of Modern Education jaise initiatives shamil the. Hyderabad ka ek aur mahatvapurn pehlu uska software aur IT industry ka vikas hai, jismein 1990s ke ant tak **HITEC City** ka vikas aur **Cyberabad** ke roop mein iska vishwabhar mein prasiddh hona shamil hai. Aaj Hyderabad ek sanatan sheher hai jo apne itihaas, sanskriti aur adhunik vikas ka ek adbhut mishran hai.
